    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>Boston</placeName>
                <date>Oct: 23/623</date>
            </p>
            <p>Rev &amp; Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Yours duly recd and have to inform you that <persName>Mr
                    Spier</persName><lb/> gave the same answer as before:
                    “<persName>Philip</persName> has recd <hi rend="underline">none</hi>”
                    <date>Sunday</date> I think<lb/> in the first meeting of the School before whom
                you claim will be presented,<lb/> and as soon I will receive it I will forward
                it.</p>
            <p>In regard to the Church they intend purchasing I can only say that there<lb/> is no
                earthly possibility to do anything but making the entrance at <add>מזרח</add><lb/>
                where it is now, and the <add>היכל</add> either direct <hi rend="underline">North
                    East</hi> or <hi rend="underline">North West</hi><lb/> the latter is the most
                probable side; as for Reformers I do not care,<lb/> I only care for the fanatics
                    <add>צבועים</add>...I believe the Hamburger<lb/> Synag. at
                    <placeName>London</placeName> is neither placed <add>לצד מזרח</add> and believe
                it to be on<lb/> the North East, I am not sure; as I stated I am lacking<lb/>
                <add>?</add> books <add>אין אמון בלא כל</add> but I would say if you would
                discuss<lb/> the matter with some conversant in our Laws, or having the
                required<lb/> books, you would perceive that I am right to authorize the<lb/>
                Trustees, under the existing circumstances to do it. <persName>Mr
                    Ettinger</persName>,<lb/>
                <persName>Mr Pape</persName> Old <persName>Mr Heilprin</persName>
                <add>אחרון חביב</add> are able to decide the<lb/> matter, they will find no
                difficulty whatever. I have ordered<lb/> some books from
                    <placeName>Europe</placeName> and will soon be out of my troubles</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">You will confer a great favor on me to attend to it at<lb/> your
                earliest convenience. If purchased no messenger<lb/> or <add>ראפאל</add> you will
                officiate <add>ביני ובינך</add>. I will look for that.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">The <sic>are</sic> resolutions passed touching myself &amp; Son
                shall<lb/> I send them to you or to the <add>מבשר</add>? There are some notes of
                private<lb/> individuals which mys be written over, send me word how to do</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">Yours Truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">
                <persName role="author">Simon le Noot</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
